 2023-04492023-05-18HC
ActTobacco and Vaping Products Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the Tobacco and Vaping Products Act
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE TOBACCO AND VAPING PRODUCTS ACT in order to permit the use of colouring agents to whiten the tipping paper of cigarettes, little cigars that have a filter, and tubes where a white background for the health warning would be required.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2023-0098 Publication Date: 2023-06-07
